108
00:07:51,330 --> 00:07:53,620
untuk memulai hidup yang baru.

109
00:07:53,620 --> 00:07:55,460
Benar, Ayah.

110
00:07:55,460 --> 00:07:57,380
Kau ingat beberapa waktu
lalu dalam perjalanan...

111
00:07:57,380 --> 00:08:00,130
Ayah bertemu Tn.
Francis Tremaine.

112
00:08:00,130 --> 00:08:01,340
Ya.

113
00:08:01,340 --> 00:08:04,220
Ketua Serikat Mercer, bukan?

114
00:08:04,220 --> 00:08:05,720
Dulunya.

115
00:08:05,720 --> 00:08:07,840
Dia sudah meninggal.

116
00:08:08,390 --> 00:08:10,310
Jandanya...

117
00:08:11,390 --> 00:08:13,390
seorang wanita terhormat...

118
00:08:13,390 --> 00:08:15,690
kini sendirian...

119
00:08:15,690 --> 00:08:18,480
walau usianya masih cukup muda.

120
