Cepat, Tn. Angsa!

1033
01:11:22,010 --> 01:11:23,720
Ayo!

1034
01:11:26,980 --> 01:11:29,100
Hati-hati, Tn. Angsa!

1035
01:11:33,190 --> 01:11:34,650
Astaga!

1036
01:11:43,620 --> 01:11:45,160
Kau!

1037
01:11:45,160 --> 01:11:47,120
Berhenti atas nama raja!

1038
01:11:47,540 --> 01:11:49,540
Waktu yang buruk.

